Package com.centurylink.mdw.services.event

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ServiceHandler
    Abstraction of a Service processor so that other handlers such as Camel routes can register to respond to MDW listener requests.
    WorkflowHandler
    Abstraction of a workflow processor (analogous to an adapter activity) that can be registered to perform actions in response to a step in a process flow.
